　　11　　月　　25　　日\r\n　　　　　　　　　　　　　檢　察　官　  許宏緯","JFULLPDF":"https://data.judicial.gov.tw/jdg/api/JDocFile/PCDM/110%2c%e7%b0%a1%2c4964%2c20220224%2c1/pdf"},"JID":"PCDM,110,簡,4964,20220224,1","JYEAR":"110","JCASE":"簡","JNO":"4964","JDATE":"20220224","JTITLE":"妨害自由"}